India reported 10,064 new #coronavirus cases with 137 #COVID19 deaths in the last 24 hours.
It is the lowest rise of cases since June-2020 & lowest deaths since May-2020.
Total confirm cases have reached to 10,582,647 with 152,593 deaths & 10,228,753.
